{"tid":800687,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"開車玩「抖音」釀車禍 淡定女成身血繼續玩手機","createTime":"2018-08-31T05:33:53.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-31T08:42:57.000Z","uid":75969,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"94b94de0f071d50d73ddfe0950d13d71b025bcf0","tid":800687,"uid":75969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-31T05:33:53.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=zfdX5mpCwp8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DzfdX5mpCwp8&d=2w%2Bf58oZeIvkdAHGcO9PKxFQyUQXuyYblCT5RSyYNoQ%3D&h=ea24ac2e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=zfdX5mpCwp8</a><br />\n<br />\n自從內地推出短視頻應用程式「抖音」後，深受不少年輕人喜愛。杭州近日有女子在開車期間玩「抖音」，導致車禍，私家車撞向馬路邊護欄，她受傷等候救援期間，仍然堅找玩「抖音」。<br />\n<br />\n事發在28日下午1時許，浙江杭州市30多歲女子在開車期間用「抖音」拍攝影片，從影片中可見副駕駛座上有其愛犬。期間她為躲避馬路上的狗，急忙向右轉方向盤，並撞向護欄。護欄插入車前方引擎蓋，再貫穿到後方擋風玻璃。幸插入位置偏中間，未有刺中女事主，她頸椎部分地方骨折，臉部多處受傷，未有生命危險。<br />\n<br />\n途徑路人見狀協助報警，並上前幫忙。當時女子滿臉血並十分虛弱，但仍然繼續用手機。<br />\n<br />\n有網民在微博留言表示關心，「狗沒事吧」。亦有人批評「開車還用手機是傻了嗎」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://std.stheadline.com/instant/articles/detail/804805\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstd.stheadline.com%2Finstant%2Farticles%2Fdetail%2F804805&d=2w%2Bf58oZeIvkdAHGcO9PKxFQyUQXuyYblCT5RSyYNoQ%3D&h=f74a5f0c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstd.stheadline.com%2Finstant%2Farticles%2Fdetail%2F804805&h=e4a518e5\" target=\"_blank\">http://std.stheadline.com/instant/articles/detail/804805</a>"},{"pid":"c381ed1cda08170c528182a1bf47feb7e18df9d3","tid":800687,"uid":170229,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-31T08:28:30.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">有網民在微博留言表示關心，「狗沒事吧」</span>"},{"pid":"a41f374c29787c134e5cd3fd6fa21f9d5794488d","tid":800687,"uid":799,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-31T08:29:39.000Z","msg":"大陸玩手機 玩呢d社交媒體真係著左魔, d人好撚空虛寂寞咁款<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e0fc7a